  "render_html": "<ul><li>一、测试环境：</li><li>二、修改频率方法：</li><li>三、测试过程及结果</li><li>四、测试2</li><li>五、fullstack3498上的测试<ul><li>1、MHA</li><li>2、GQA</li></ul></li></ul><h2>一、测试环境：</h2><p>full stack： 1718</p><p>机器： 10.50.32.252</p><p>测试代码： Files · mha_decoder_batch_pipline_GMB_3eu · Zheng Li(李政) / supa-test · JiHu GitLab (birentech.com) （未上库）</p><p> batch pipline + QK输出到GMB + 3EU</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2>二、修改频率方法：</h2><p>方法1:</p><p>git clone  https://github01.birentech.com/software/br_debug</p><p>--build：</p><blockquote>./build.sh</blockquote><p>-- usage：</p><p>Get help info by the command below:</p><blockquote>./gpu_debugger -h</blockquote><p>更改以及查看spc频率命令：</p><p>sudo ./gpu_debugger --get_spc_clock<br>sudo ./gpu_debugger --set_spc_clock 1000</p><p>方法2：</p><p> sudo brsmi gpu set -p 1<br> sudo brsmi gpu set --pclk 800<br> cat /sys/class/biren/card_0/device/core_clock</p><h2> 三、测试过程及结果</h2><p>&nbsp;</p><p>1 测试的case:</p><p>MHA_test&lt;FP32&gt;(1, 1, 32, 32, 511, 1);<br>MHA_test&lt;FP32&gt;(1, 1, 32, 32, 575, 1);<br>MHA_test&lt;FP32&gt;(1, 1, 32, 32, 639, 1);</p><p><br>MHA_test&lt;FP32&gt;(8, 1, 32, 32, 511, 1);<br>MHA_test&lt;FP32&gt;(8, 1, 32, 32, 575, 1);<br>MHA_test&lt;FP32&gt;(8, 1, 32, 32, 639, 1);<br><br>MHA_test&lt;FP32&gt;(16, 1, 32, 32, 511, 1);<br>MHA_test&lt;FP32&gt;(16, 1, 32, 32, 575, 1);<br>MHA_test&lt;FP32&gt;(16, 1, 32, 32, 639, 1);<br><br>MHA_test&lt;BF16&gt;(1, 1, 32, 32, 511, 1);<br>MHA_test&lt;BF16&gt;(1, 1, 32, 32, 575, 1);<br>MHA_test&lt;BF16&gt;(1, 1, 32, 32, 639, 1);<br><br>MHA_test&lt;BF16&gt;(8, 1, 32, 32, 511, 1);<br>MHA_test&lt;BF16&gt;(8, 1, 32, 32, 575, 1);<br>MHA_test&lt;BF16&gt;(8, 1, 32, 32, 639, 1);<br><br>MHA_test&lt;BF16&gt;(16, 1, 32, 32, 511, 1);<br>MHA_test&lt;BF16&gt;(16, 1, 32, 32, 575, 1);<br>MHA_test&lt;BF16&gt;(16, 1, 32, 32, 639, 1);</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>2 测试方法</p><p>记录spc频率为1000M, 800M, 500M, 250M时的 cbi cycle (max )</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>3 测试结果</p><div class=\"doc-table-wrap\"><table class=\"doc-table\"><tr><td rowspan=\"2\"><p>&nbsp;</p></td><